---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="studio — jka">
  <section class="studio-manifesto-plate">
    <p class="manifesto">we remove what does not belong. what remains is architecture: pure line, honest structure, and natural light given room to define the space on its own terms.</p>
  </section>
  <div class="silence-threshold"></div>
  <section class="studio-section settle">
    <div><span class="tag-index">a</span><span class="tag-name">holistic<br>authorship</span></div>
    <p class="section-copy">jka does not design a shell and hand it over. every commission is authored as one continuous work — from the reading of the site's topography, through the structural grid, the calibration of light and aperture, the interior architecture, down to the lacquer on a single cabinet door. we hold this line because a space is experienced whole, not in disciplines. the furniture is not placed in the room; it is resolved from the same logic that shaped the room. this is the difference between decorating a building and authoring one. the work is finished only when nothing remains to remove.</p>
  </section>
  <div class="studio-hairline"></div>
  <section class="studio-section settle">
    <div><span class="tag-index">b</span><span class="tag-name">provenance<br>&amp; longevity</span></div>
    <p class="section-copy">jka was founded in beirut in 1998. nearly three decades of practice across lebanon, the levant, and the gulf have built something no young studio can claim: accumulated judgement. we have navigated complex sites, demanding geographies, and the exacting standards of private clients across the region — and delivered through every condition the region has asked of us. beirut taught the discipline; the gulf refined the scale. this longevity is not a number on a page. it is the quiet assurance behind every drawing: that the practice has seen the problem before, and knows precisely what does not belong in the answer.</p>
  </section>
  <div class="silence-major"></div>
  <section class="studio-grid settle">
    <div>
      <div class="col-head first">practice</div>
      <div class="grid-item">architecture</div>
      <div class="grid-item">interior architecture</div>
      <div class="grid-item">bespoke product design</div>
      <div class="col-head">selected recognition</div>
      <div class="grid-item dim">award-winning product design</div>
      <div class="grid-item dim">press — [populates from cms]</div>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-block">
      <b>enquiries</b>mail@jihadk.com<br><br>
      <b>parameters</b>private residential, workplace, and retail commissions — lebanon, the gulf, and beyond. each engagement begins with a conversation, not a brief.<br><br>
      <b>studio</b>riverside 2404, sin el fil, beirut · est. 1998
    </div>
  </section>
